{"tid":1468110,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[割席的真正意義] 我中文唔算好，點解你班人仲差過我","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:12:17.000Z","uid":229916,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"39404219986fe5bbe8253d59ef6a52114ac04969","tid":1468110,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:26.000Z","msg":"成班人係度話人地割席，知唔知咩叫割席，割席係膽拖<strong>絕交</strong>. 家陣都冇人話要絕交<br />\n<br />\n今日係做得唔完美，有意見好正常，屌多幾句都唔係罕見，但是屌者，都冇話割席，割席絕交個隻割席呀！！！！<br />\n<br />\n我只係想大家唔好見人屌兩句就話割席<br />\n做得唔好咪改囉，都冇人話唔改，打左場仗兩個月，我地都係錯誤中成長架啦<br />\n<br />\n對家見你地內鬨唔知幾開心！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n計我話全力一致，聽日再塞爆機場又好，道歉又好，叫律師黨JR 張禁制令又好，集中火力團結返啦please!!!!!"},{"pid":"f45a43466e9843b77664f406b76346073217ce8e","tid":1468110,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:36.000Z","msg":"推五次"},{"pid":"a97216189408e03ce57b6231d90e213737c654e9","tid":1468110,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:57:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3883bc0641f9221c026364252f83ba89130bca49","tid":1468110,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9291077d2e8a1fe055c0ca9539aca0dbf3324a94","tid":1468110,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1e83eb154605acb25717fdd97752509e3a5aa2","tid":1468110,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7fab127b8659135bcf0d54f3684f2b731911af1","tid":1468110,"uid":263311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:58:32.000Z","msg":"啱啊"},{"pid":"b7b5a88c3b32b4ed9b4bace463a25206999fd577","tid":1468110,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"